Text: RE smubetas SETI via eWooglinDo I see another reenactment of the infamous eWooglin dorg Maybe an all new version of the weakest link aka The Shepin the making for prime time TV Like Bro Storhtz and some others recently on our trips to Dallas Hope everyone has a great homecoming wish Wheeler I could be there We have a special invitation for all Betas Our company will be having our annual
